These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, water, iced-tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, marigold, dahlia
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, february, july
1. the colombian is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the indonesian is between the person drinking water and the person drinking iced-tea##2
3. the colombian is the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking water##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | iced-tea   | almond-milk  | water  |
| Flower   | azalea    | dahlia    | iris      | marigold    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Birthday     | july  | october       | april    | february     |

