.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
4 different games are played: go, backgammon, snooker, whist
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, bartender, engineer, software-developer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, daffodil, tulip
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the software-developer is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person playing whist is between the engineer and the person who growsrose##2
6. the person who growstulip is between the person playing whist and the software-developer##2
7. the journalist is on the far right##1
8. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person playing snooker is on the right of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Game   | go      | backgammon  | whist  | snooker |
| Job           | software-developer      | engineer       | bartender      | journalist       |
| Flower         | balloon-flower    | tulip | daffodil | rose |

