.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, april, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, ebony, azure, red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, horror, crime, sports
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person watching crime movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who likes red##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who likes amber and the person who likes red##2
9. the person who likes azure is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person watching horror movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Birthday        | june | april     | january   | december     |
| Color       | ebony   | amber   | azure | red |
| Movie-Genre         | drama   | crime | sports       | horror    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

