 6. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the australian##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is between the fonseca-smoker and the person playing chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Game           | scrabble  | chess | mah-jongg     | monopoly |
