 3. the person playing poker is the person drinking cola##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person drinking tea is between the fan of d&b and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage          | cola         | tea         | water     | 7up      |
| Game           | poker | mah-jongg | canasta    | monopoly     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep     | house       | d&b | gospel |

