The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, trike, bus
1. the fan of folk is between the person driving the bus and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person watching western movies is between the fan of folk and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person driving the roller and the owner of the frog##2
4. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the far right##1
9. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre           | sports | western | drama  | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | punk       | folk     | jazz      |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | frog      | guinea-pig   | pony   |
| Transport         | trike   | bus    | snowmobile | roller   |

