 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person playing billiard is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
